original_title: Jessie J: Alive at the O2
overview: This was the first headline arena tour for the star, after the release of her second studio album Alive in September, and from a BRIT school budding starlet to proper international superstar, Jessie electrified the O2 stage for an impressive 1.5 hour, 18-track, 5-costume filled set. The gig was divided into five sections and themes, including Love, Instinct and Values.
title: Jessie J: Alive at the O2
